---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Writing | Shiqing Gao"
  description="Low-key learning notes and project reflections by Shiqing Gao."
  lang="en"
>
  <header class="container page-header personal-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">Writing</p>
    <h1>Notes before they become polished conclusions.</h1>
    <p>
      This page is reserved for learning notes, project reflections, and short
      explanations. I will only add posts when they are complete enough to be
      useful publicly.
    </p>
  </header>

  <section class="container writing-empty section">
    <div class="writing-index" aria-hidden="true">W-01</div>
    <div>
      <h2>A quiet holding page, not a filled-out blog.</h2>
      <p>
        Future notes may include reflections on inverse problems, numerical
        experiments, uncertainty quantification, and modeling workflows. For now,
        the main public content lives on the project pages and CV.
      </p>
      <p class="english-note">
        This area is intentionally secondary to the academic project pages.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
